      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything is gone. the crash took the whole company overnight. i’m looking at millions in debt and i don't even know how to tell my family. i can't face them. i just can't stand the thought of them looking at me like i'm some kind of joke. i've never felt this much shame in my entire life.",
